{"id":441465,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":21}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"170","ytitle":"","mtitle":"节约标兵","ftitle":"","authors":["何信豪"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海汽车电机厂　何信豪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"材料员老张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年五十开外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你经手过多少材料?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排一排，比那长江长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧社会你给老板当差，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勾勾划划记一笔糊涂眼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新社会你当材料员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的的!嗒嗒!算盘子做文章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"废铁堆上你常去作客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾刀头，捡洋圆，觅宝一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时你会跟踪零件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批评浪费材料的组长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说你文化低?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记还夸你算术不差，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小处入手往大处想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为社会主义算大账。"}]}